OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778674273
OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FThousands of people gathered in
OL,7,Fcentral London to protest against
OL,8,Frising levels of antisemitism and to
OL,9,Fcall on the Government to do more to
OL,10,Fprotect British Jews.
OL,12,FProtesters were waving Israeli flags,
OL,13,Fthe Union flag, Iranian protest flags
OL,14,Fand holding protest placards.
OL,16,FSome signs say "British Jews deserve
OL,17,Fbetter", "where is Keir" and "Brits
OL,18,Fagainst antisemitism".
OL,26,@xD@POUyD@GO]yD@JOUyD@XO]yD@^OUzD@UO]
