CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778674273
OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FOfficials from the government, the
OL,7,FConservative party, the Liberal
OL,8,FDemocrats and Reform were all invited
OL,9,Fto address the rally.
OL,11,FZack Polanski, leader of the Green
OL,12,FParty, was not asked to attend.
OL,14,FIn an open letter, two thousand
OL,15,FBritish Jews called for Nigel Farage's
OL,16,Finvite to be withdrawn, to ensure the
OL,17,Fevent would reflect values of
OL,18,Finclusion and solidarity."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
