PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778674273
OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,7,FMcFadden was jeered and booed as he
OL,8,Fspoke at the rally.
OL,10,FOn stage at the rally, Mr McFadden
OL,11,Fsaid: "I come to speak for something,
OL,12,Ffor freedom, for the freedom that
OL,13,Fmarks us out as a great country."
OL,15,FProtestors shouted "shame", "it's your
OL,16,Fparty's fault", "when will you act"
OL,17,Fand "Jew harmer" at the Labour
OL,18,Fpolitician.
OL,26,@sD@GOUuD@aO]wD@TOUwD@ZO]wD@]OUxD@NO]xD@
OL,26,AQOUxD@cO]yD@EOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
