OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778674273
OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FAs his voice was drowned out by the
OL,7,Fboos, Mr McFadden said: "Friends, I
OL,8,Fhear you, I am with you, I am here to
OL,9,Ffight antisemitism."
OL,11,FPoliticians from across the spectrum
OL,12,Fspoke at the rally, with Kemi
OL,13,FBadenoch, leader of the Conservative
OL,14,FParty, receiving huge applause as she
OL,15,Ftook the stage.
OL,26,@oD@YOUqD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
