OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FShe said: "Many of you know that I was
OL,7,Fborn in this country, but I grew up in
OL,8,FNigeria, and in 2014, I remember when
OL,9,F300 schoolgirls were stolen from their
OL,10,Fschool by Islamic extremists, and only
OL,11,Fa few returned.
OL,13,F"I remember on October 7, I saw that
OL,14,Fsame terror, the murder and the
OL,15,Fmassacre of young people at a music
OL,16,Ffestival.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
