PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778674273
OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,F"There are many, many different
OL,7,Fpockets of antisemitism in this
OL,8,Fcountry, but I am most worried about
OL,9,Fthe growth of extremism and terror
OL,10,Faround the world and how it targets
OL,11,Fmany groups in this country.
OL,13,F"Britain has been a sanctuary for
OL,14,FJewish people, and it must always be a
OL,15,Fsanctuary for Jewish people."
OL,17,FKemi Badenoch, alongside other
OL,18,Fpoliticians, called for the Iranian
OL,19,FRevolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC) to be
OL,20,Fbanned as a terrorist organisation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
