OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FRichard Tice, deputy leader of Reform
OL,7,FUK, said:
OL,9,F"What we need is action.
OL,11,F"We need to ban and proscribe the
OL,12,FIRGC, we are sick of them. Get them
OL,13,Fout of our country."
OL,15,FMr Tice added: "The scourge of
OL,16,Fantisemitism has been allowed to
OL,17,Fflourish in our beloved country, and
OL,18,Fwe have to say we are sick and tired
OL,19,Fof warm words from waffly politicians.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@AOUuD@TO]wD@POU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
