PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778674273
OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,F"We need to take on the failure of
OL,7,Fleadership in our universities. Maybe
OL,8,Fwe should say to the universities, if
OL,9,Fyou allow this to carry on, forget any
OL,10,Fform of grants. Forget any form of
OL,11,Fstudent loans. Forget any form of
OL,12,Fresearch funding."
OL,14,FThe latest rally comes after two
OL,15,FJewish men were stabbed in Golders
OL,16,FGreen on April 29.
OL,18,FBoy George, who previously said he had
OL,19,Fbeen left "in tears" following the
OL,20,Fstabbings, sent a video message of
OL,21,Fsupport for the attendees.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@RO]{D@KOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
