OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778674273
OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FIn the aftermath of the Golders Green
OL,7,Fassaults, he said he had received
OL,8,Fabuse online over his messages of
OL,9,Fsolidarity with the Jewish community.
OL,11,FIn a pre-recorded message, the singer
OL,12,Fsaid he wished he had been able to
OL,13,Fattend the event, saying "Not only for
OL,14,Fthose amazing Jewish people, but also
OL,15,Fpeople who support their Jewish
OL,16,Ffriends".
OL,18,FHe added: "People like me keep being
OL,19,Fthanked for speaking up for Jewish
OL,20,Fpeople. I don't want to be thanked for
OL,21,Fdoing what is right.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUxD@HO]zD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
