PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1778674273
OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,F"I have so many Jewish friends and
OL,7,Fknow some would be there today, but
OL,8,Feven if I don't know you, I send you
OL,9,Fmy love, and I hope today we send a
OL,10,Fpowerful message to the entire world.
OL,12,F"God bless you all and have the most
OL,13,Famazing event."
OL,15,FThe event, organised by the Jewish
OL,16,FLeadership Council and the Board of
OL,17,FDeputies of British Jews, was attended
OL,18,Fby "over 20,000", according to
OL,19,Fspeakers at the rally.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@OO]zD@DOUzD@PO]
