OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FStrict security measures were in place
OL,7,Fwith attendees going through airport
OL,8,Fstyle security, with metal detectors
OL,9,Fand bag searches, at the Trafalgar
OL,10,FSquare entrance to Whitehall.
OL,12,FThe Metropolitan Police announced this
OL,13,Fweek a community protection team of
OL,14,F100 extra officers to help to
OL,15,Fsafeguard the Jewish community,
OL,16,Fdespite Sir Mark Rowley's previous
OL,17,Fcall for 300 extra police officers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
