OL,3,CThousands gather outside Downing
OL,4,CStreet for protest against antisemitism
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police Commissioner
OL,7,Fwarned of a growing "pandemic" of
OL,8,Fantisemitism in the UK and said he is
OL,9,F"very concerned" about the
OL,10,Fsustainability of the force's current
OL,11,Fapproach to protecting Jewish
OL,12,Fcommunities in the capital.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
